the txt is to introduce of v2ray install method in ubuntu system.

server need to install v2ray,and client is same method.
----------------------------------
wget https://install.direct/go.sh
----------------------------------

and then,we need to rewrite config txt
-------------------------
vi /etc/v2ray/config.json
-------------------------

next,we need to start it,it is do in server. 
----------------------------
sudo systemctl start v2ray
sudo systemctl stop v2ray
sudo systemctl restart v2ray
----------------------------


if your are ubuntu14.04 clinet,
your need to install on same method,
but if your want to run it ,your need to 
go to the v2ray and run it.
-----------------------
cd /usr/bin/v2ray
./v2ray -config /etc/v2ray/config.json
-----------------------
your can use commod follow
-------------------------

